824
01:00:54,570 --> 01:00:58,800
a right dagger on the vacuum.

825
01:00:58,800 --> 01:01:07,740
And that has Lz equals 2 h bar.

826
01:01:07,740 --> 01:01:12,900
And therefore, you must have--
