938
01:08:15,670 --> 01:08:20,210
So a couple of things
about hydrogen.

939
01:08:24,000 --> 01:08:32,290
So hydrogen H is
equal to p squared

940
01:08:32,290 --> 01:08:38,450
over 2m minus e squared over r.

941
01:08:38,450 --> 01:08:43,979
There's a natural length scale
